properties.City: On our first experience at Bilkent Labs, we're cheerful,hope this continuos likewise. This was the caption of my instagram post in the Bilkent Labs using an oscillisocope for the first time. Though there has been sleeples nights in those labs throughout four years of my Bachelors degree, the feeling when I received my Bachelor of Science degree is unspeakble after four years of hustling. I was the type of person who had to go home after a nighout because I had to study... Sure, having graduated with an honors degree was a source of joy and satisfaction, but more, much more than this I did it my way!
